{
  "stem": "24466.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they call-- they were the Nationalists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the killers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning there were some uniforms, too, from the police, from the army, from the ghetto army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But most of them, they were in civil, carrying white, white bands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Arm bands.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I left-- I believe-- I don't remember that quite rightly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember that quite rightly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Straight away, killings of Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were killing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were assembling them in the [NON-ENGLISH], in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] They were the one before the [GERMAN] came to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were the one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the killers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were the one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were-- they called them harpoonists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were the one, that they were doing the-- all, all, all killings of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Killings?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the ghetto-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but that would-- most probably, I will tell you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] Instead to go to the ghetto, because the ghetto was full-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] so the unlucky people, they were herded in the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] jails.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there were horrible things there done, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I witness, for instance, in the cell, where [INAUDIBLE] 30 or 40 people, there was about 200 or 250 people there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one lady, elderly lady, took her life by taking some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] drugs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what that was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because you ask me if I was close to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when they start to knock through the door that a person is dying, and so on, they came in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was that [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said like this-- now [SPEAKING GERMAN] And he took out from-- a revolver and give it [INAUDIBLE] and kill her.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
